title: Collective Evolution
cleaned_text:
At Collective Evolution we believe our world is in a time of change and transition. New ways of designing our societies to care for nature, humans, and our commons are necessary.

We believe in order to do this we must focus on the health and wellbeing of individuals in order to build a solid foundation for sustainable change. In essence, we must address individual and collective trauma as it's paramount to why our society functions the way it does.

To build a thriving world, we have to thrive. To transform our world, we have to transform.

Thus, Collective Evolution has focused for on 2 key avenues for the last 15 years:
